<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Online Examination Portal</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
        }
        .button {
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #007bff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Online Examination Portal</h1>
        <p>Your one-stop solution for managing and taking exams online. Whether you're an educator or a student, we have the tools you need to succeed.</p>
        <div class="buttons">
            <a href="/Educator" class="button">I'm an Educator</a>
            <a href="/Student" class="button">I'm a Student</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
